OL,3,CMan groomed children on Snapchat and
OL,4,Cused them to deal drugs around town
OL,6,FA man from Swindon who groomed
OL,7,Fchildren on Snapchat and used them to
OL,8,Fdeal drugs on his behalf around the
OL,9,Ftown has been jailed for more than
OL,10,Ffive and a half years.
OL,12,FKyum Raham, 23, formerly of Northern
OL,13,FRoad, Rodbourne Cheney, trafficked his
OL,14,Fthree teenage victims, all aged 16 and
OL,15,Funder, and used them as drug runners.
OL,17,FRaham exploited the teenagers by
OL,18,Frecruiting them through Snapchat and
OL,19,Fthen groomed them by offering them
OL,20,Fcash.
