OL,6,FHe was sentenced to five years and
OL,7,Fseven months at Swindon Crown Court on
OL,8,FThursday, 22 January, following an
OL,9,Finvestigation by Wiltshire's Serious
OL,10,FOrganised Crime Unit (STPO).
OL,12,FHe was also handed a 10-year Slavery
OL,13,Fand Trafficking Prevention Order.
OL,15,FDetective Inspector Champion of the
OL,16,FSerious Organised Crime Unit said:
OL,17,F"This STPO is a significant
OL,18,Fachievement which recognises the risk
OL,19,Fthat Raham poses, both while in prison
OL,20,Fand when he is released.
