OL,6,F"The order will require Raham to keep
OL,7,Fpolice immediately informed of any
OL,8,Fchanges of addresses, provide his
OL,9,Fsocial media account details, register
OL,10,Fhis mobile phones and prohibit any
OL,11,Funsupervised contact with any person
OL,12,Funder the age of 18, including online.
OL,14,F"He is a predator who exploited the
OL,15,Fvictims for his own gain, tempting
OL,16,Fthem with money and arranging their
OL,17,Ftravel around Swindon to deal drugs on
OL,18,Fhis behalf.
